{"tid":1783394,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲飲過碘水醫甲亢","createTime":"2019-12-14T18:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T07:31:03.000Z","uid":239266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0bdaf546e98bf00d12c53827dd2b3c0fcef23707","tid":1783394,"uid":239266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:09:05.000Z","msg":"前二次keep住食綠色藥丸仔降甲亢指數 <br />\n穩定之後停藥同覆診抽血<br />\n今日睇醫生甲亢第三次復發<br />\n醫生建議我去飲碘水治療或者做手術<br />\n希望可以斷尾<br />\n因為再食藥都有大機會復發<br />\n而家甲亢藥又有副作用<br />\n最終都決定排期飲碘水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係度想問下飲過碘水嘅巴絲<br />\n<br />\n飲完碘水之後會有副作用，<br />\n但係會唔會好嚴重同體重會急升？<br />\n<br />\n飲完一定要同屋企人隔離？<br />\n隔離幾耐呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以斷尾？<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思講到1999<br />\n真係好擔心，<br />\n唔該哂各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e05241023834f379cfda4af1b328158f928ea74","tid":1783394,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:10:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推，今日既行動post</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a77EG51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa77EG51.jpg&h=a86f9171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z7yo8L2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ7yo8L2.jpg&h=242df1ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmC9jSP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmC9jSP.jpg&h=8bedeaeb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f753627816152ca25206306a1d03c024a66c47a","tid":1783394,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:12:16.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a10f75509fd32cc787e277a6c449557805599b1","tid":1783394,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:25:32.000Z","msg":"想知呢個病有咩病徵?"},{"pid":"b7e58531598446e003f87ca91678483e0c872096","tid":1783394,"uid":239266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a10f75509fd32cc787e277a6c449557805599b1","tid":1783394,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:25:32.000Z","msg":"想知呢個病有咩病徵?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:39:30.000Z","msg":"心跳加快<br />\n手震 無力<br />\n出汗<br />\n好容易攰<br />\n月經唔正常<br />\n突然食極唔肥/體重急升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你屋企人曾經患過甲亢<br />\n咁機會率又會高啲"},{"pid":"0e71cb4589b069d367075d0b516d909c1e4a0798","tid":1783394,"uid":239392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:45:35.000Z","msg":"飲過3次。頭7日唔好接觸小朋友，行房可免則免，最好分開訓。食飯用公筷。無事盡量留港，因為過關會響機，由其是返大陸，萬一要離港，最好攞定醫生紙証明做過放射性治療。飲嘅時候無乜特別，同飲水一樣，都無乜副作用，大致上就係咁。"},{"pid":"9092e97d12fd923526793573e40bb79879e61137","tid":1783394,"uid":263366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:46:00.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借一借個位<br />\n［行動post]入黎睇！一個真正經濟攬炒既平安夜<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35a173e1e640461283d05eee74c931392751ec39","tid":1783394,"uid":36942,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"b7e58531598446e003f87ca91678483e0c872096","tid":1783394,"uid":239266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a10f75509fd32cc787e277a6c449557805599b1","tid":1783394,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:25:32.000Z","msg":"想知呢個病有咩病徵?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:39:30.000Z","msg":"心跳加快<br />\n手震 無力<br />\n出汗<br />\n好容易攰<br />\n月經唔正常<br />\n突然食極唔肥/體重急升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你屋企人曾經患過甲亢<br />\n咁機會率又會高啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:46:32.000Z","msg":"有無試過嚴浩食療？